onPHP feature list (still and always incomplete)
================================================
- $Id$ -

	core/Cache/

		Universal multi-peer weight-based cache support. Currently
		supports Memcached and RubberFileSystem with or without
		ReferencePool wrapper, and offers PlainDatabase class as an
		example of cache peer.

	main/DAOs/

		{Generic,(Smart|Common)}DAO:
			basic yet powerful tools for building DAO's
			hierarchy.

	main/Containers/

		StorableContainer and UnifiedContainer:
			handling of identifiable objects collections.
		
	core/DB/

		DB, {Pg,My,MS,Ora}SQL, {ANSI,Postgres,My,MS,Oracle}Dialect:
			database abstraction layer.

	core/Exceptions/

		Bunch of very useful exceptions. ;-)

	core/Form/

		HTML forms' data checking and validation tools. Supports rules 
		based on logical expressions, data filtering, etc.
	
	core/Logic/

		Logical expressions used in OSQL and Form.

	main/Module/

		Quite common tools for implementing MVCv2::Controllers.

	core/OSQL/

		{Select,Insert,Update,Delete}Query:
			SQL query builders.
	
	main/Template/

		Easy template package. Main [and single] aim is incapsulation
		of template variables.
		Separation of view and model should be done on language level.

	main/Utils/

		Random accompanying utilities.
